      <dt class="news-tit ellipsis" data-level=""><a target="_blank" href="http://news.sina.com.cn/gov/xlxw/2018-09-13/doc-ihkahyhw6678938.shtml">五年来习近平这样论述“一带一路”</a></dt>
	  
            <dd class="news-con col1">
        <a class="news-img" target="_blank" href="http://news.sina.com.cn/gov/xlxw/2018-09-13/doc-ihkahyhw6678938.shtml">
          <img alt="五年来习近平这样论述“一带一路”" src="http://k.sinaimg.cn/n/news/crawl/587/w550h8037/20180913/C5Id-hiixpun8020446.jpg/w180h135l50t1053.jpg">
        </a>
        <div class="news-des">
           <p><span node-type="summary">　　原标题：五年来习近平这样论述“一带一路”
</span><a class="CC-theme" target="_blank" href="http://news.sina.com.cn/gov/xlxw/2018-09-13/doc-ihkahyhw6678938.shtml">[详情]</a></p>
